file.name: swagger-bare-bones.yml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Bakery
  license:
    name: MIT
components:
  securitySchemes:
    BearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
x-swagger-bake:
  components:
    schemas:
      app-exceptions:
        ValidationException:
          x-exception-fqn: '\MixerApi\ExceptionRender\ValidationException'
          type: object
          properties:
            exception:
              type: string
              example: ValidationException
            message:
              type: string
              example: Error saving resource `Schema`
            url:
              type: string
              example: /url/path
            code:
              type: integer
              example: 500
            violations:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/x-swagger-bake/components/schemas/app-exceptions/Violation'
        Violation:
          type: object
          properties:
            propertyPath:
              type: string
              example: property_name
            messages:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/x-swagger-bake/components/schemas/app-exceptions/ViolationMessage'
        ViolationMessage:
          type: object
          properties:
            rule:
              type: string
              example: _rule_name
            message:
              type: string
              example: error message
    parameters:
      paginatorPage:
        name: page
        in: query
        required: false
        schema:
          type: integer
      paginatorLimit:
        name: limit
        in: query
        required: false
        schema:
          type: integer
      paginatorSort:
        name: direction
        in: query
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
      paginatorDirection:
        name: direction
        in: query
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
